        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://apr.sagepub.com/cgi/content/abstract/34/3/341">The Daily Show Effect: Candidate Evaluations, Efficacy, and American Youth</a></h4>

        

        <p>&#8220;Overall, the findings &#8230; show that for young people, no other news source drives cynicism toward the candidates and the political system more than The Daily Show.&#8221;</p>

