<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/oct/19/">&#x27a0;</a> October 19, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="hearfromyourmpcom" >

        
        <a name="002064"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.hearfromyourmp.com/">HearFromYourMP.com</a></h4>

        

        <p>&#8220;Sign up to hear from your MP about local issues, and to discuss them with other constituents&#8221;.  Fantastic idea.  Build up a captive audience for your MP, effectively forcing them to speak to you, then giving you a forum to discuss.</p>

